Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:06.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\an8}光る宝石の欠片集めて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.25,0:02:12.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\an8}両手広げれば青く輝くの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.95,0:02:19.29,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\an8}やけに眩しくて　瞳封じたの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:25.81,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\an8}触れた唇　遠い日の記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.23,0:02:32.68,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\an8}さりげない　優しさでも惑わずに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.91,0:02:39.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\an8}運命だって諦めずに　変えてみせる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:46.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\an8}翼をひろげて　手と手を取り合えば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.96,0:02:53.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\an8}雲の上さえ　歩ける気がする
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:03:00.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\an8}アナタのいる今　耐え難い過去もない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.31,0:03:07.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\an8}無数の光からキミを導く

Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:06.06,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}收集耀石之碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.25,0:02:12.50,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}舒展双臂 青光闪烁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.95,0:02:19.29,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}彩霞耀眼 封闭眼瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:25.81,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}碰触双唇 往昔记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.23,0:02:32.68,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}若无其事　不以温存而困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.91,0:02:39.90,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}不以命运而放弃　使其改变
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:46.75,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}假使放飞双翅 两手相牵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.96,0:02:53.42,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}则将漫步云端 应有可期
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:03:00.13,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}如今有你　忧伤过往将化为乌有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.31,0:03:07.56,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}无数光芒将执君向前

Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.88,0:23:00.95,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}就算在雨天乘着巴士出行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.79,0:23:07.86,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}你依旧一脸不开心地漫步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.69,0:23:14.91,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}若我取悦你 你会露出笑容吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.54,0:23:21.25,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}一起去创造理想的世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.01,0:23:28.66,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}在梦中说尽不满
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.02,0:23:35.91,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}我喜欢空想的浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.32,0:23:43.96,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}童话中也没有永远
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.19,0:23:49.42,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}就算公主也会生气
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.11,0:23:53.96,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}童话的一页
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.36,0:24:05.09,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}翻开崭新一页的便是你了

Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.88,0:23:00.95,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\an8}雨降るバスでお出かけしても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.79,0:23:07.86,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\an8}あなたは不機嫌なままで歩く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.69,0:23:14.91,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\an8}ご機嫌取ると笑顔になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.54,0:23:21.25,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\an8}理想の世界を作って行ける
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.01,0:23:24.94,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\an8}夢の中の出来事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.47,0:23:28.66,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\an8}不満ばかりを言って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.02,0:23:35.91,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\an8}妄想のロマンス私は好きだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.32,0:23:43.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\an8}おとぎ話の中でも永遠なんてない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.19,0:23:49.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\an8}お姫様だってカンカンよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.11,0:23:53.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\an8}おとぎ話の一ページ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.36,0:24:05.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\an8}新しいページをめくれるのはそうあなた

Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.09,0:00:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}森里：羽田 到了这时候别害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.09,0:00:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}明日香：…… 什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.47,0:00:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}两年半以前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.09,0:00:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}森里：直说了 他想要和你交往
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.10,0:00:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}鹰志：不行啊。为什么 这样……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.16,0:00:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}鹰志：咦？ ……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}来交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.69,0:00:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.55,0:00:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}学生们：唉～～～～～～～～～～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}你是羽田同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}我是渡来 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.53,0:00:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}嗯 我才应该
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}虽然你说跟着我 我要跟你去什么地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.37,0:00:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}吃饭？买东西？妇产科？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.14,0:00:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}那不是那样的 是森里他们突然提起让我向你告白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.51,0:00:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}是这样啊 那么再见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.60,0:00:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.42,0:00:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}不是… 由我来说也有点那啥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.29,0:00:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}我想大家都误会了 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.50,0:00:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}男女朋友的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:00:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}嗯 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}你知道的吗 那么为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.49,0:01:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}因为看你挺可怜的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.28,0:01:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}还有被朋友当做被欺负一方也挺可怜的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.31,0:01:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}被欺负… 讨厌啊 不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}那个只是稍稍的玩笑 大家能够高兴就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.58,0:01:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}那么我做了多余的事了 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.16,0:01:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}没 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.59,0:01:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}不 这并不好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.78,0:01:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}这样的话渡来还在被误解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.04,0:01:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}羽田有喜欢的女孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.39,0:01:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}没什么特别在意的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.64,0:01:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}那就好了 那暂时就这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.29,0:01:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.78,0:01:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}这就是距今两年半以前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.94,0:01:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}羽田鹰志和渡来明日香的\N说不上恋爱开端的恋爱开端

Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.99,0:03:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}鹰公卿是如此品德高尚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.99,0:03:22.94,ZS2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15\pos(627,967.5)}Hawk

Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.23,0:03:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}诶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}不是「诶」吧 你刚才偷窥了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}不是的 别胡说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:03:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}哈？ 是谁在胡说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}你刚不还畅快地看呢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}你颤抖着说什么呢 变态
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.31,0:04:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}嘛 无所谓 这种辩解不要对我说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}去对本人或者学生指导员去说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}等等 请听我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.85,0:04:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}竟然在这种时候召唤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}明明不解开和这个人误会不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}怎么了 发出这么吵闹的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}这家伙刚刚偷看前辈的内裤来着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.08,0:04:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}他说不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}啊？是啊 被抓到的痴汉大家都会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}不管怎么说这个人没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}男朋友男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}嘛 姑且算是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:04:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}啊哈哈 吵到你对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}不 不是… 话说我才是失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}不是对我 对他道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.81,0:05:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}还是老样子心胸开阔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.69,0:05:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}为什么不生气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.22,0:05:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}因为他也不是有恶意 想生气也生不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}不可理喻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}什么的 这就是羽田同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.29,0:05:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}话又说回来你看我内裤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}唉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}看到了就杀了你 如果说谎也杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}羽田
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.84,0:05:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}高内同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.26,0:05:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}那啥 班主任说差不多该准备
