Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}召唤的间隔日渐变短了 而且还不分时间地点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}快要结束了吧 我得做好觉悟了

Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}好冷 好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.24,0:14:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}抱歉 我没注意到你在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}好过分 哥哥老是这样坏心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.71,0:14:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}总之先开灯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.59,0:14:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}好刺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:14:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}对、对不起 我现在就关掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.97,0:15:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.43,0:15:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}小鸠 快把衣服穿好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}衣服？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.49,0:15:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}谁？ 那个 在这房子里的只有你和我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.01,0:15:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}被看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.30,0:15:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}不 没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.91,0:15:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}快穿上衣服的好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.71,0:15:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}嗯 我就是要这样做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}是吗 今年的风变化无常 要注意点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.18,0:15:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}谢谢 我会注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.69,0:15:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}嗯 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:15:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}和妹妹一直不自然 明明每天都见面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.28,0:16:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}这样就像好久不见了表兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.51,0:16:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}我不在了也不会感到伤心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}您好 我是羽田
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}大晚上真是打扰了 我是美空学园三年级A班的渡来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}请问鹰志在家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.33,0:16:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}差不多就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.89,0:16:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}嗯 帮上大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}但是怎么了 突然打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}这并不奇怪吧 我们正在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}但 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.34,0:16:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}还是说你有喜欢的女孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}羽田同学还没找到喜欢的女孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}难道在介意我吗 我可以毫不在意的被你甩掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:17:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}到了那时大概… 可能稍微有点寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}你在听吗 羽田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.95,0:17:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}你这样子看来还没呢 真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.99,0:17:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}女朋友是不能这么说的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}是呢 啊哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}也好 那么谢谢了 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}嗯 晚安

