Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.74,0:17:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}所以我也想让大家协力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.23,0:17:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}大家请听听我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.37,0:17:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}好 今天解散
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.67,0:18:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}高内同学 你擅自…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}在期末说这种事也是无用功
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}我说你丫稍微给我思考一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.78,0:18:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}为什么这样的人在当班长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.18,0:18:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}鹰・青蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.21,0:18:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}我记得你是Princess明日香的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}是的 我每天照顾她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.97,0:18:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}我知道你的眼瞳一直注视着明日香大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.76,0:18:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}但是就请在云掩藏住月亮的少许涣散间给予我慰藉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.13,0:19:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}无名的侍女啊 我无法接受你的心意 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}请不要这么说 现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.94,0:19:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}请就在此时作为只属于我的鹰 恳求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.37,0:19:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}我 我有… 咦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.13,0:19:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}高内 意外你很有料啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.52,0:19:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}这是和谁比 果然是明日香大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.47,0:19:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}讨厌呀 我还没和明日香做过那种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.05,0:19:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}胡说 真的？ 那我还有空可插啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.74,0:19:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}啊哈哈… 这怎么说好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}虽然搞不太懂 但是这不是很难吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.48,0:19:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}你这算什么 都脱光求你了还这样不是很过分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}话说真的很受打击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.44,0:19:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}话说高内的那个不是胸垫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.88,0:19:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}决不是 纯正天然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}你有木面不改色地说着很过分的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.89,0:19:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}我说有你丫这样呶呶不休地说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:19:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}真是个难题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.74,0:20:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}你看 每个人都有立场和设定什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}不好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}对不起 我无法回答你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.03,0:20:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}此身此心都…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}不行吧 这不行吧 不会随波逐流的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.95,0:20:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}说的也是呢

