Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.50,0:20:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}这种日子也有 换换心情了没
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.18,0:20:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}是吗 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.11,0:20:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}下次就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}如果没问题的话我有个想让你陪我买东西的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.23,0:20:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.50,0:20:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}下次就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.12,0:20:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}嗯 近期的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.53,0:20:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.97,0:20:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}太好了 没被拒绝 紧张死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.03,0:21:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}我不可能拒绝的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.66,0:21:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}诶 可是羽田一直在避开我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.76,0:21:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}没有这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.15,0:21:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.54,0:21:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}都做了两年半的男朋友一次也没邀过我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.88,0:21:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}这样一般都会认为被避开了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}不是的 那是渡来先…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.89,0:21:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}我基本上是个「讨厌世俗」的人\N没有跟任何人交往的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.95,0:21:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}但是不断拒绝别人\N就会被平白无故地憎恨和怀偏见不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.02,0:21:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}所以作为我来说\N和羽田同学这样被人误解比较方便
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}稍微等等 稍微等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.08,0:21:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}那么说我明明没被讨厌却被无视了两年半吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.16,0:21:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}我说你 想约我的话就约我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.22,0:21:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}就算觉得不行也没有放手一搏的秉性吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.97,0:21:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}我还没怒你却怒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.89,0:21:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}才不是 我发火理所当然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.75,0:21:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}怎么想都是我应该生气 最初的原因就是因为渡来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.09,0:21:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}说来我和羽田同学的条件就是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.05,0:21:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}条件是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.62,0:22:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be15}{\Mai_tubasa}我是女孩子
